spells.description:
Use: Take what is rightfully yours, gorging on your target's essence to deal 3.3 million Shadow damage and healing you for 493,381 over 2 sec. Damage and healing increased based on the target's missing health.

Cooldown reduced by 60 sec if this effect kills the target. (2 Min Cooldown)

Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 1.6 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 78,773  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Taking damage greater than 25% of your health grants you 2,449 Avoidance and increases healing taken by 10% for 10 sec. This effect may only occur every 90 sec.

Falling damage reduced.
